The '''Fifth Alderaanian Expedition''' was the fifth in a series of exploratory expeditions originating from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. It was this survey group that discovered [[Hijarna]] and attempted to catalog its history.

